spec_data.Name: perl-Getopt-Usaginator
spec_data.Description:
Getopt::Usaginator is a tool for creating a handy usage subroutine for
commandline applications. It does not do any option parsing, but is best paired
with Getopt::Long or any of the other myriad of option parsers.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 11:57:36 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Conjure up a usage function for your applications
